============================================
Description:                               =
============================================

Play Ashley Clark 2 - The Secrets of the Ancient Temple and solve an unusual murder! 6 months ago a veterinarian was found dead in a zoo. The place has been almost completely abandoned since, but now there's another unusual death. One of the security guards. What's happening in this zoo and who or what is responsible?

============================================
FEATURES:                                  =
============================================

Step in the shoes of a detective and solve a curious creepy case 
Explore lots of exciting hidden object scenes and complete many challenges 
Crack clever puzzles and finish other amazing mini-games during your investigation 
Enjoy a captivating plot and unexpected twists and mysteries

